{% block physics_section %}
MOVEMENT
You can move in 8 directions: N, S, E, W, NE, NW, SE, SW. Moving into a wall
does nothing (you stay in place, no penalty).

The following actions are no-ops in Room-5x5 (kept for MiniHack suite consistency):
WAIT, SEARCH, LOOK, PICKUP, APPLY, INVENTORY, ESCAPE.

NOTE
The agent (@) and stairs (>) are placed randomly each episode. Plan your path
after observing the grid.
